{"tid":2275612,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"GFRIEND 發片倒數兩天！即將首度舉行回歸秀","createTime":"2020-11-07T09:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T16:51:09.000Z","uid":16659,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"480f7d806f27c825b2f86b55804ae5aef7579829","tid":2275612,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T09:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_0a213eab23eb098a9d358196d9efef3b/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-07/131476-883772.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_0a213eab23eb098a9d358196d9efef3b%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-07%2F131476-883772.png&h=e214c488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下週一 GFRIEND 就會帶著睽違一年十個月的正規專輯回歸，這一次她們也將首度在發片當晚立刻舉行回歸秀！<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_8d49a91c6046c977893b1ebb2357f4e7/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-07/131476-883773.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_8d49a91c6046c977893b1ebb2357f4e7%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-07%2F131476-883773.jpg&h=4fba99e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource Music 昨天下午公開了《GFRIEND COMEBACK SHOW &ldquo;回:Walpurgis Night&rdquo;》的預告片，宣布她們將於 9 日晚間 8 點（韓國時間）透過 SBS MTV 直播回歸秀。<br />\n<br />\n除了在回歸秀上首度公開表演最新主打歌 &ldquo;MAGO&rdquo; 外，久違地發表正規專輯的 GFRIEND，也會分享製作〈回:Walpurgis Night〉時的幕後故事，同時透過這種線上活動與世界各地的 Buddy 即時互動。<br />\n<br />\n最近 GFRIEND 已公開〈回:Walpurgis Night〉中所有歌曲的亮點集錦，以及走復古風的主打歌 &ldquo;MAGO&rdquo; MV 預告片。下週一別忘了準時鎖定她們的回歸囉！<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：Source Music）"},{"pid":"75a68c38160fcf468b47c052e51162c244971eee","tid":2275612,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T09:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1024x0/?fname=https://t1.daumcdn.net/cafeattach/1YmK3/095f20161eec9814b85db85c5fd32bd6df840b77\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.daumcdn.net%2Fthumb%2FR1024x0%2F%3Ffname%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Ft1.daumcd